Deputy Head of House Nengi has defined her relationship with Kiddwaya as platonic. She said this during a discussion with Head of House, Ozo during a conversation on day 37. Nengi stated she might be playful around Kiddwaya but they are only friends and nothing more. Speaking further, Nengi said Kidd is the only guy that matches her energy in the House. “Kidd is just like my play partner. Don’t take us seriously at all. He’s the only person that matches my energy. We’re just friends,” she told Ozo.